{
  "name": "link-safe",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "連結安全檢查",
  "category": "P",
  "number": 311,
  "pain_point": "防 Phishing 連結檢查",
  "commercial": "⚠️",
  "language": "Python",
  "dependencies": [
    "requests",
    "click",
    "rich"
  ],
  "agent_compatible": true,
  "mcp_ready": true,
  "intent_triggers": [
    "這個連結安不安全，幫我掃描一下",
    "我收到一封郵件裡有個可疑連結",
    "檢查這個 URL 是不是釣魚網站",
    "幫我批次驗證這些連結的安全性",
    "這個縮短網址點了會不會有風險",
    "掃描文件裡所有 URL 是否有惡意連結",
    "這個 domain 是不是假冒的"
  ],
  "examples": [
    {
      "query": "檢查 http://suspicious-site.com/login 是否為釣魚連結",
      "params": {
        "url": "http://suspicious-site.com/login"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "批次掃描 urls.txt 裡所有連結的安全性",
      "params": {
        "input_file": "urls.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "掃描 email_body.txt 中所有 URL 並標記可疑連結",
      "params": {
        "input_file": "email_body.txt",
        "extract_urls": true
      }
    }
  ],
  "params_schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "extract_urls": {
        "type": "boolean"
      },
      "input_file": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "url": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    }
  },
  "license": "MIT"
}
